CHILDSAFE has been selling anti-drowning pool fences in Canada for more than 30 years. CHILDSAFE fence is weather resistant and easily removable.
see-through mesh allows for easy surveillance and is also very aesthetic. ChildSafe exceeds the safety requirements to prevent drownings and the standards ASTM F2286-16 of excellence in the market.

Specializing in the sale and installation of residential pool fences in Canada, we are proud to say that we have built our reputation on the excellence of our service and our attention to detail.
Personalized and to your budget, the projects carried out by Child Safe Pool Fence will meet your highest expectations.

Child Safe removable and permanent pool fences. Professional services. Quality products. You will have peace of mind around your inground pool, above ground pool, and any other body of water.
